[b][color=#88ff00]Check out my new survival PVP project [/color][url=https://www.armyrust.com][color=#88ff00]ARMYRUST[/color][/url]

[heading]DESCRIPTION[/heading]
Climbable skyscraper with a view of all of Skyrim and water below
Tallest building in Tamriel
Extreme challenge for anyone who considers themself agile
Great for experiments with pushing people off, throwing things, diving etc

Located on an island in Falkreath lake
[url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/images/28501-1-1356685791.jpg]Map location[/url]

Currently need help to make LOD for this

[youtube]1B8WThNnmj4[/youtube]

Update 1.1 : Improved drop architecture
